      <title>欧洲央行霍尔兹曼警告称，今年不能保证降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/davos-2024-holzmann-warns-no-one-should-bank-on-ecb-rate-cuts-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挥之不去的通胀威胁将阻止欧洲央行今年降息——理事会成员罗伯特·霍尔兹曼表示，即使不能再排除经济衰退的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/davos-2024-holzmann-warns-no-one-should-bank-on-ecb-rate-cuts-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:34:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
